2000-01-02  Peter Pointner  <peter@wuzel.m.isar.de>

	* configure.in: disable qt build by default. --enable-qt enables it.

	* Makefile.in: new targets qt.static and qt.disable

	* make-gnucash-patch: exclude *.moc

